{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans came in, and I remember so vividly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was standing in the window and looking down the market, because we lived just next to the-- next to the market.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived in the first floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked down, and I see people coming and going in a much larger number that what we usually saw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my parents came up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said the news just came through that the Germans invaded Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and a-- a strange feeling came on me, like-- I hope the word is correct-- like a intuition-- that there is something going to happen to me, or-- or this occupation is going to affect me some-- some way.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I'm not a religious Jew, but a very gut-feeling, and very gut-believing guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from then on-- it-- it sounds stupid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But whatever happened to me in my life, it happened that I got-- not a sign from God, but I got something telling me to do something which I wouldn't do it ordinarily, which led my life from that moment on, right up today.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that means my deportation to concentration camp, to coming home, to start playing football, to leave Hungary, to leave to Australia, to start a business here, to sell business here.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I always got something from up there, which-- which didn't say to me with words, but said to me with something that you do this now, because that's what-- what you have to do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and whatever happened to me in the past, and whatever going to happen me in the future, I do-- when I have this-- [LAUGHS] this signal.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in good Jewish custom-- touch wood-- it never let me down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
